1) run 'install' to install tools required for runtime and compilation of software
2) run 'cfg_v4l' to configure video card (see code in case of problems)
3) run 'video' to test if card wroks (5s mplayer window - camera image should be visible)
4) build sources with 'cd software && make'
5) run 'start' to start robot's software and debugging windows, showing what's going on in the system (ctrl+C breaks processing)
6) run 'reset' to kill all processes and stop the robot
